<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَارِزَةً}</span> ... ظَاهِرَةً لَيْسَ عَلَيْهَا مَا كَان يَسْتُرُهَا مِنَ المَخْلُوقَاتِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحَشَرْنَاهُمْ}</span> ... جَمَعْنَاهُمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَمْ نُغَادِرْ}</span> ... لَمْ نَتْرُكْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَفًّا}</span> ... مُصْطَفِّينَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَوُضِعَ الْكِتَابُ}</span> ... كِتَابُ أَعْمَالِ كُلِّ وَاحِدٍ فِي يَمِينِهِ، أَوْ شِمَالِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يُغَادِرُ}</span> ... لَا يَتْرُكُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
