<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَفَسَقَ}</span> ... فَخَرَجَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَوْلِيَاءَ}</span> ... أَعْوَانًا تُطِيعُونَهُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَضُدًا}</span> ... أَعْوَانًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّوْبِقًا}</span> ... مَهلِكًا فِي جَهَنَّمَ يَهْلِكُونَ فِيهِ جَمِيعًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
